snippet.title: [UE4] Import custom sets into The Bricksperience V2.0
snippet.description:
The Bricksperience on itch.io: https://dasmatze.itch.io/the-bricksperience

LDraw: http://www.ldraw.org/article/104.html

LDraw-compatible software:
https://www.lego.com/en-us/ldd/download
https://studio.bricklink.com/v2/build/studio.page
http://www.melkert.net/LDCad/download
http://mlcad.lm-software.com/
https://www.leocad.org/download.html

Music from Jukedeck - create your own at http://jukedeck.com.
